This paper focuses on efficient 360° perception for autonomous systems, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO). The proposed approach uses self-supervised learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI). Additionally, the paper introduces novel techniques for processing 360° images, which could fall under computer graphics (GR). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.GR.
